{"tid":2001993,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【大行報告】花旗：本地樓價5月回升 今年升最多10%","createTime":"2020-05-05T02:49:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T04:57:42.000Z","uid":339805,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b89cff7c55c1bd2d19cc436770978f3435f99412","tid":2001993,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:49:38.000Z","msg":"花旗預計，本地樓價從5月份開始恢復上升趨勢，到今年年底將上升約5%至10%。<br />\n<br />\n花旗指，如果疫情能持續在中港兩地改善，香港樓價和零售銷售可能已在4月份出現谷底。又預期，如果疫情持續受控，6月初香港和內地之間的旅行限制將進一步放鬆。<br />\n<br />\n花旗認為，現時是買入收租股的好時機，因為本月開始零售業應有所改善，且股票具有吸引力。地產股中看好新地（0016）、新世界（0017），而零售業收租股當中，看好恒隆地產（0101）、九龍倉置業（1997）和希慎興業（0014）。"},{"pid":"cc33dff10108d4e5ca6f8fe5ce2e1a6a3b5303e7","tid":2001993,"uid":81698,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"仲有人信d大行預測？彈出彈入到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fef65a1c4eb3adf70a0a76a9805a6746e671b0e","tid":2001993,"uid":44646,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"cc33dff10108d4e5ca6f8fe5ce2e1a6a3b5303e7","tid":2001993,"uid":81698,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"仲有人信d大行預測？彈出彈入到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:54:55.000Z","msg":"花旗在大行中算準<br />\n(佢過去幾年都估升)"},{"pid":"f51b29ca3bb6caf631de14b91aebaae990de815e","tid":2001993,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:55:08.000Z","msg":"花旗咪撚燈呀on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次預測都錯撚晒"},{"pid":"d5bb2d351cfd68bbcc41152cde9aaa0647daa915","tid":2001993,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f51b29ca3bb6caf631de14b91aebaae990de815e","tid":2001993,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:55:08.000Z","msg":"花旗咪撚燈呀on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次預測都錯撚晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:55:52.000Z","msg":"citi燈力拍得住面神<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3b095d6eac5b9d3e6737175302a723a14bd878","tid":2001993,"uid":44783,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"花旗料下半年樓價冧20% 維持港股目標25500點<br />\n2017年06月12日11:56 最後更新: 12:29<br />\n<br />\n外資大行對本港下半年走勢看法分歧，摩根士丹利早前雖然將恒指基本預測目標，由26,000點上調至28,000點，意味還有逾8%潛在上升空間。不過，另一大行花旗卻給予港股「減持」評級，目標維持在25,500點不變，即大市已經到價。該行又預期下半年香港樓價將大跌20%，建議減持本地地產股，較看好銀行及濠賭股。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVsNznJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVsNznJ.jpg&h=70a23a45&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n17年升到18年中都未跌過"},{"pid":"0f2488bcb07f6154420c83c4cb87747e955b5d19","tid":2001993,"uid":221051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:01:14.000Z","msg":"樓市見底 步入升浪！花旗：往後樓價每個月貴1%<br />\n <br />\n樓市 on Nov 4, 2019 at 12:49<br />\n<br />\n花旗於《施政報告》公布當天曾發表報告，指樓價會較原本預期更早反彈，明年2月前或會見底。花旗集團中國香港地產研究主管楊海全近日向傳媒表示，相信樓市月內便見底，更指現時是買樓好時機，並建議主攻600萬至800萬嘅單位。CCL年初至6月高位一度累飆11%，之後回軟，現時已由高峰下調約6%並見底，估計往後每月回升1%，今年全年樓價可漲約5%，與年初預測相符。至於明年整體表現，他忘為當社會事件理順後，樓市料可恢復正常並能延續升勢，儘管下半年有機會較上半年弱，但全年計依然會上揚。"},{"pid":"67d4c9eca299f8556f4610128c2939788682d5e4","tid":2001993,"uid":221051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:04:47.000Z","msg":"兩三個月就發表一次報告意見不斷tune 黎tune 去， 咁實中<br />\n<br />\n但你買樓賣樓唔可能兩三個月就trade 一次"},{"pid":"0a549a02fc70ef83b844bcf2f76217597c443fce","tid":2001993,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:06:12.000Z","msg":"班廢炎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81b554943dd57335ab13a736e8d55c964212c70","tid":2001993,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f51b29ca3bb6caf631de14b91aebaae990de815e","tid":2001993,"uid":8880,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T02:55:08.000Z","msg":"花旗咪撚燈呀on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 次次預測都錯撚晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"呢D專家只係寫讀者想睇既野"},{"pid":"3e101e2290185b4e9c7ce66516100711753b6f9a","tid":2001993,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:10:53.000Z","msg":"專家食屎圖.jpg"},{"pid":"7de052c1745a76ed0e4965fd6cb1c09a9d06995e","tid":2001993,"uid":142588,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:27:10.000Z","msg":"點解突然轉升架， d 淡淡點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb530252cb10045aaffd21f506e88f74ec40e4b","tid":2001993,"uid":239912,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T05:27:48.000Z","msg":"花旗都係aa"},{"pid":"6fdd907cb5f5cd50474f2e191b1b8595e3050f8e","tid":2001993,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f2488bcb07f6154420c83c4cb87747e955b5d19","tid":2001993,"uid":221051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T03:01:14.000Z","msg":"樓市見底 步入升浪！花旗：往後樓價每個月貴1%<br />\n <br />\n樓市 on Nov 4, 2019 at 12:49<br />\n<br />\n花旗於《施政報告》公布當天曾發表報告，指樓價會較原本預期更早反彈，明年2月前或會見底。花旗集團中國香港地產研究主管楊海全近日向傳媒表示，相信樓市月內便見底，更指現時是買樓好時機，並建議主攻600萬至800萬嘅單位。CCL年初至6月高位一度累飆11%，之後回軟，現時已由高峰下調約6%並見底，估計往後每月回升1%，今年全年樓價可漲約5%，與年初預測相符。至於明年整體表現，他忘為當社會事件理順後，樓市料可恢復正常並能延續升勢，儘管下半年有機會較上半年弱，但全年計依然會上揚。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-06T04:57:42.000Z","msg":"冇諗過有支那肺炎"}]}